org.videolan.vlc.util

Class MurmurHash

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.videolan.vlc.util.MurmurHash

  • public final class MurmurHash
extends java.lang.Object
    Murmur hash 2.0. The murmur hash is a relative fast hash function from http://murmurhash.googlepages.com/ for platforms with efficient multiplication. This is a re-implementation of the original C code plus some additional features. Public domain.
    Version:
    1.0.2
    Author:
    Viliam Holub
